<i>noun</i>: 필요성 [피료썽], 필요 [피료] <i>verb</i>: 요하다 [요하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>필요성 [피료썽]</dt><br>
<dd>necessity; need</dd><br>
<dd>꼭 있어야 하는 성질.</dd><br>
<dd>The quality of being necessary.</dd><br>
<dt>필요 [피료]</dt><br>
<dd>need; necessity; requirement</dd><br>
<dd>꼭 있어야 함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being necessary.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>요하다 [요하다]</dt><br>
<dd>require; demand; need</dd><br>
<dd>필요로 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To be in need.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>